---
description: Core working rules for this repo
alwaysApply: true
---

This repo has multiple parts. Work carefully and keep changes scoped.

Project working rules:

- map which layer you are touching before editing: frontend, backend, config, or shared contract
- do not make unrelated changes across layers
- prefer small vertical slices over broad rewrites
- when changing API behavior, verify both backend and frontend impact
- before suggesting commands, inspect the repo and use the project’s real scripts/build files rather than guessing
- prefer existing naming, structure, and patterns already used in the repo
- keep diffs reviewable and avoid cosmetic churn
- when done, summarize exactly what changed, what to test, and any remaining risks
